Alan Campbell (screenwriter) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_Campbell_(screenwriter) 0 Alan K. Campbell (February 21, 1904 – June 14, 1963) was an American writer, stage actor, and screenwriter. He and his wife, Dorothy Parker, were a popular screenwriting team in Hollywood from 1934 to 1963.
